@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

[*] --> Register

state Register
Register : entry / new user starts registration
Register : do / collect user information
Register : exit / successful registration
Register : exit / invalid registration

state Login
Login : entry / user attempts to login
Login : do / validate credentials
Login : exit / logged in successfully
Login : exit / login failed

state "Access Facilities" as AccessFacilities
AccessFacilities : entry / user accesses facilities after login
AccessFacilities : do / provide access to available services
AccessFacilities : exit / end of session

state NewsAndContent
NewsAndContent : entry / user reads news and expert content
NewsAndContent : do / display content
NewsAndContent : exit / continue using system or finish session

state SymptomChecker
SymptomChecker : entry / user checks symptoms or uses fitness options
SymptomChecker : do / provide health-related information
SymptomChecker : exit / continue using system or finish session

state InsuranceProcessing
InsuranceProcessing : entry / process and validate insurance for finance services
InsuranceProcessing : do / complete payment with insurance
InsuranceProcessing : exit / payment completed

state PaymentSelection
PaymentSelection : entry / user selects payment method (cash or insurance)
PaymentSelection : do / display payment options
PaymentSelection : exit / proceed to payment

state CashDetails
CashDetails : entry / inform user about cash payment details
CashDetails : do / provide cash payment information
CashDetails : exit / continue using system or finish session

state InsurancePayment
InsurancePayment : entry / complete insurance-based payments
InsurancePayment : do / finalize payment process
InsurancePayment : exit / payment completed

state FeedbackCollection
FeedbackCollection : entry / collect user feedback after service completion
FeedbackCollection : do / gather feedback
FeedbackCollection : exit / end of session

state Logout
Logout : entry / user logs out at the end of their session
Logout : do / log out user
Logout : exit / successfully logged out

Register --> Login
Login --> AccessFacilities
AccessFacilities --> NewsAndContent
NewsAndContent --> SymptomChecker
SymptomChecker --> InsuranceProcessing
InsuranceProcessing --> PaymentSelection
PaymentSelection --> CashDetails
CashDetails --> InsurancePayment
InsurancePayment --> FeedbackCollection
FeedbackCollection --> Logout
Logout --> [*]

@enduml
